Introduction

iii is a pre-debut South Korean girl group formed by BIG OCEAN E&M. The group plans to debut in the first half of 2024. The group consists of Nicole, Ahra, and Yan. The group name 'iii' comes from the word 'in•spir•ation'.

iii released their pre-debut digital single 'Forbidden Midnight' on November 22nd, 2023. Both Vivi and Evie left Big Ocean E&M and iii sometime in early to mid-2024.
